perf tools: Introduce perf_callchain_config()

This patch adds support for following config options to ~/.perfconfig file.

  [call-graph]
    record-mode = dwarf
    dump-size = 8192
    print-type = fractal
    order = callee
    threshold = 0.5
    print-limit = 128
    sort-key = function

